snippet.title: Cover Your Eyes - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Out now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1188290/Cover_Your_Eyes/

"Cover your eyes is a newly released 16-bit survival horror game, focusing upon family, and the sacrifices we make to keep them safe. Chloe and her two children will embark on a journey to find her missing husband before the whole town descends into hell."
